cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.DC, cs.DB 

This paper is about automated machine learning (AutoML) systems, which are typically studied in the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the optimization of machine learning pipelines, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper analyzes a large database of pipelines, which is related to databases (cs.DB).
